OL,3,CPolice 'considering left-wing motive'
OL,4,Cin Ann Widdecombe murder probe
OL,6,FCounter-terrorism police are probing
OL,7,Fwhether the suspect held over Ann
OL,8,FWiddecombe's killing was motivated by
OL,9,Fleft-wing extremism and planning
OL,10,Ffurther violence against other high-
OL,11,Fprofile figures.
OL,13,FDetectives confirmed Miss Widdecombe's
OL,14,Fdeath was a "targeted attack", and
OL,15,Fsaid whether the suspect in the
OL,16,Falleged murder was targeting Reform UK
OL,17,Ffigures will be a "line of
OL,18,Finvestigation".
OL,26,@vD@MOUvD@]O]yD@SOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
