OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784081888
OL,3,CPolice 'considering left-wing motive'
OL,4,Cin Ann Widdecombe murder probe
OL,6,FThe police investigation is also
OL,7,Fprobing whether left-wing extremism or
OL,8,Fother political motives were behind
OL,9,Fthe killing, it has been reported.
OL,11,FThe 78-year-old former MP and MEP was
OL,12,Ffound dead at her home in Haytor on
OL,13,FDartmoor, Devon, on Thursday.
OL,15,FA 28-year-old white British man
OL,16,Farrested in South Yorkshire on
OL,17,FSaturday remains in custody.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
