FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784081888
OL,3,CPolice 'considering left-wing motive'
OL,4,Cin Ann Widdecombe murder probe
OL,6,FHe is being held on suspicion of
OL,7,Fcommission, preparation, or
OL,8,Finstigation of acts of terrorism, as
OL,9,Fwell as on suspicion of murder.
OL,11,FCounter-terrorism police are now in
OL,12,Fcharge of the case after new evidence
OL,13,Fcame to light ` but a senior officer
OL,14,Fstressed the murder and terror
OL,15,Finvestigations are currently working
OL,16,F"in parallel".
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
