OL,3,CPolice 'considering left-wing motive'
OL,4,Cin Ann Widdecombe murder probe
OL,6,FAssistant Commissioner Laurence Taylor
OL,7,Ftold reporters on Tuesday the question
OL,8,Fof whether a TV appearance might have
OL,9,Fmotivated her killing is also a "line
OL,10,Fof inquiry".
OL,12,FMiss Widdecombe spoke to Mark Dolan by
OL,13,Fvideo-link on Talk TV just after 8am
OL,14,Fon Wednesday, and police believe she
OL,15,Fwas attacked at about 12.30pm the same
OL,16,Fday.
OL,18,F"It is clear that this was a targeted
OL,19,Fattack," Mr Taylor said.
OL,26,@qD@aOUrD@KO]zD@AOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784081888
OL,3,CPolice 'considering left-wing motive'
OL,4,Cin Ann Widdecombe murder probe
OL,6,F"We are still working to understand
OL,7,Fthe extent of any planning or
OL,8,Fpreparation, and the motivation that
OL,9,Fsits behind that attack."
OL,11,FAsked if police were probing whether
OL,12,Fthe suspect was targeting other Reform
OL,13,FUK figures, he said: "So clearly, part
OL,14,Fof our responsibility when
OL,15,Finvestigating offences of this nature
OL,16,Fis to assure ourselves and therefore
OL,17,Fthe public and others of any extant of
OL,18,Fthreat.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@YO]uD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784081888
OL,3,CPolice 'considering left-wing motive'
OL,4,Cin Ann Widdecombe murder probe
OL,6,F"That will form a line of
OL,7,Finvestigation to ensure that we are
OL,8,Fputting all appropriate measures in
OL,9,Fplace to mitigate any threat, should
OL,10,Fit become apparent.
OL,12,F"I'm not saying there is or there
OL,13,Fisn't at this stage."
OL,15,FIncoming prime minister Andy Burnham
OL,16,Fsaid after the update that a "serious
OL,17,Freview" was needed into MPs' security.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@UO]xD@^OUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784081888
OL,3,CPolice 'considering left-wing motive'
OL,4,Cin Ann Widdecombe murder probe
OL,6,FHe said: "It's obviously appalling
OL,7,Fwhat happened to Ann. I knew Ann over
OL,8,Fmany years in the House, and you know,
OL,9,Fwe would get along ` and everybody
OL,10,Fwould get along.
OL,12,F"But it feels as though something has
OL,13,Fchanged. It's easy to blame social
OL,14,Fmedia, but it feels like it's having
OL,15,Fsome impact in just building that kind
OL,16,Fof toxicity that's around the
OL,17,Fpolitical debate."
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784081888
OL,3,CPolice 'considering left-wing motive'
OL,4,Cin Ann Widdecombe murder probe
OL,6,FMr Burnham said the issue could not be
OL,7,Fsolved by "easy, glib answers,"
OL,8,Fadding: "I do think we need now a
OL,9,Fserious review of MPs' security.
OL,11,F"I certainly am prepared to do that."
OL,13,FMiss Widdecombe's death follows the
OL,14,Fmurders of Conservative MP Sir David
OL,15,FAmess in 2021 and Labour's Jo Cox in
OL,16,F2016.
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@_O]pD@IOUsD@AOUsD@eO]
